lead_paragraph: Sheldon McClellan scored 22 points and Ja'Quan Newton hit a huge 3-pointer to lead No. 17 Miami to its fifth win in six games, 75-68 over Georgia Tech on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: McClellan, Newton Lead No. 17 Miami Past Georgia Tech 75-68
